{"tid":2249651,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"嗇色園預祝百周年 黃大仙祠監院高呼愛國：我唔理任何政治宗教 淨係記得我係中國人","createTime":"2020-10-19T13:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T15:26:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"16eea7ffbda52bae17446da02f15ebd5b27a093d","tid":2249651,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:00:31.000Z","msg":"明年是嗇色園黃大仙祠創立的100周年，嗇色園今（19日）舉行紀慶倒數啟動禮，為開幕典禮倒數100天。是次活動邀請黃大仙民政事務專員黃智華擔任嘉賓，嘉賓之一的黃大仙祠監院李耀輝（義覺）道長致辭時，指專員的名字含「智者、中華」令他能短時間內記得，又稱「我唔理任何嘅政治、宗教⋯⋯我淨係記得我係中國人」、「『華』係中華個『華』，所以我記得佢個名。」<br />\n<br />\n他笑言活動前不認識黃智華的名字，「唔好意思講句黃專員，我對你嘅名字都係半個鐘頭前先識」，又稱黃智華名字有「福蔭」，因名字中含有「智者、中華」的意思，令他能短時間內記住，「我唔理任何嘅政治、宗教...我只記得一樣，我係中國人」、「『華』係中華個『華』，所以我記得佢個名。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/VXCMGNSW45AQXMKKHGQCS3JYGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FVXCMGNSW45AQXMKKHGQCS3JYGI%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=f07d53cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FVXCMGNSW45AQXMKKHGQCS3JYGI%2F&h=33d8ddec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/VXCMGNSW45AQXMKKHGQCS3JYGI/</a>"},{"pid":"c39468a625ee19c97b0706bf153edf207dbf80b6","tid":2249651,"uid":21545,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"黨性最大"},{"pid":"6cd2b435011fcfba4990714ed7e3fb673b7e68ef","tid":2249651,"uid":279333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:02:08.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee358dbec78c5e230700926eab81a35eb673198","tid":2249651,"uid":11291,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"唔再理宗教嘅話咁你仲喺黃大仙祠把撚"},{"pid":"17554c51f8a1ae920a706f4be0f42450dd9b764d","tid":2249651,"uid":48362,"like":3,"dislike"